<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-purple);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Sectors</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Commercial Offices &amp; Workplace</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">From Cat-A landlord works to a fully-fitted Cat-B workplace, an office touches every one of our trades at once. We bring MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works together under <strong>one accountable team</strong> — so the services, the space and the building hand over on the same date.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about office projects →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What offices need</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One team for the<br>whole workplace.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span><a href="/meph/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">MEPH</a></span></h4><ul><li>HVAC, comfort cooling &amp; ventilation</li><li>Power, lighting &amp; small power</li><li>Structured data &amp; comms rooms</li><li>Metering &amp; energy efficiency</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span><a href="/commercial/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Commercial Fit-out</a></span></h4><ul><li>Cat-A and Cat-B fit-out</li><li>Partitions, ceilings &amp; joinery</li><li>Finishes, branding &amp; FF&amp;E</li><li>Fire-stopping &amp; compartmentation</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span><a href="/fabric/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Fabric</a></span></h4><ul><li>Façade repair &amp; recladding</li><li>Glazing &amp; curtain walling</li><li>Roofing &amp; weatherproofing</li><li>Thermal upgrades to Part L</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Landscaping</a></span></h4><ul><li>Forecourts, entrances &amp; public realm</li><li>Car parks &amp; surfacing</li><li>Planting &amp; soft landscaping</li><li>Boundaries &amp; street furniture</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What matters in offices</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Programme, compliance<br>and the move-in date.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Built around the workplace</span></h4><ul><li>BCO Guide to Specification</li><li>Cat-A / Cat-B sequencing</li><li>Out-of-hours, phased works in live buildings</li><li>BREEAM / SKA-aware delivery</li><li>Wellbeing, acoustics &amp; air quality</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Compliance, handled</span></h4><ul><li>CDM 2015 throughout</li><li>Building Regs Parts B, E, M &amp; L</li><li>BS 7671 electrical certification</li><li>Fire-stopping records for the safety case</li><li>Full O&amp;M and as-built documentation</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Office projects,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you do both the fit-out and the M&amp;E?</summary><p>Yes — that’s the point of using us for an office. MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works are self-delivered under one team and one programme, so the services and the space hand over together.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you work in an occupied office, floor by floor?</summary><p>Yes. Most workplace projects are phased around a live building — out-of-hours isolations, temporary services and floor-by-floor handover — so the business keeps running while we work.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>What’s the difference between Cat A and Cat B?</summary><p>Cat A is the landlord’s base finish — services, ceilings and raised floors; Cat B is the occupier’s fit-out on top — partitions, joinery, finishes and FF&amp;E. We deliver both, and the transition between them.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you hit a fixed move-in date?</summary><p>Yes. We pin long-lead items at design stage and run a buildable programme with one project manager accountable for the date — the fixed point we plan back from.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>We deliver office and workplace projects across London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Our service lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class=